# UI Components & Design System

## Button Variants
```typescript
// Primary: <Button variant="default">Save</Button>
// Secondary: <Button variant="secondary">Cancel</Button>
// Destructive: <Button variant="destructive">Delete</Button>
// Ghost: <Button variant="ghost">Link</Button>
// Sizes: "3xs" | "2xs" | "sm" | "default" | "lg"
// Icon: size="icon" | "icon-sm" | "icon-xs"
```

