## Color System (use CSS variables)
```css
/* Primary: */ bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary-hover
/* Secondary: */ bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground
/* Muted: */ bg-muted text-muted-foreground
/* Destructive: */ bg-destructive text-destructive-foreground
/* Background: */ bg-background bg-card bg-popover
```

## Typography
```css
/* Titles: */ .comet-title-xl, .comet-title-l, .comet-title-m, .comet-title-s
/* Body: */ .comet-body, .comet-body-s, .comet-body-xs (-accented variants)
/* Code: */ .comet-code
/* Layout: */ .comet-header-height, .comet-sidebar-width, .comet-custom-scrollbar
```

## Component Placement
- **Reusable**: `components/shared/` folder
- **Page-specific**: Same folder as parent component
- Check `components/ui/` and `components/shared/` before creating new

## Dark Theme Support
```typescript
// ✅ Theme-aware
<div className="bg-card text-card-foreground border-border">

// ❌ Hard-coded colors
<div className="bg-white text-black border-gray-200">
```

Add new colors to `main.css` with both light and dark variants:
```css
:root { --my-color: 210 100% 50%; }
.dark { --my-color: 220 100% 60%; }
```

